    },
    {
      title: "Monitored, fault-tolerant lines",
      text: "Continuously monitored loudspeaker circuits and standby power so a single cable or amplifier fault is reported and does not silence a whole zone."
    },
    {
      title: "Commissioning and documentation",
      text: "Intelligibility measurements, zone plans and a cause-and-effect matrix handed over as a defensible record for insurers, consultants and authorities."
